                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 text-center sm:text-left">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Foto Profil</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Fitur upload foto akan segera hadir. Saat ini menggunakan inisial nama Anda.</p>
              <button type="button" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors cursor-not-allowed" disabled>
